# Active Directory User Management Lab

This lab demonstrates common help desk tasks involving user account management in Active Directory, including account lockouts, password resets, and account control.

---

## 🛠️ Tasks Performed

### Account Lockout Testing
- Attempted multiple failed logins
- Configured Group Policy lockout threshold
- Observed account lockout behavior

### Account Recovery
- Unlocked user account
- Reset user password
- Verified successful login

### Account Management
- Disabled user account
- Tested login failure
- Re-enabled account
- Verified access restored

### Log Analysis
- Reviewed security logs on Domain Controller
- Observed authentication events on client machine

---

## 💡 Skills Demonstrated

- Active Directory User Management
- Group Policy Configuration
- Account Lockout Policies
- Password Reset Procedures
- Troubleshooting Login Issues
- Event Viewer Log Analysis

